data.description: Cute as a button! This 3 bedroom home sits in a great location- a block off Hardy St and across from Hattiesburg Zoo and the new water park! Minutes from USM, midtown, and downtown! Perfect home for first time home buyers or investors! Spacious great room and kitchen offers substantial cabinet and countertop space.  Extra room that is perfect for a sunroom or enclosed porch area. New exterior paint and 2 new natural gas heaters. Schedule your showing today!
